//! Markdown content generation for synthetic notes.
//!
//! Goal: produce text that is *structurally* representative of a real
//! Tesela mosaic — outline blocks, properties, wikilinks, tags — without
//! being meaningful prose. Generated bytes are deterministic given a
//! seed, so benches are reproducible.

use crate::rng::{chance, pick, range, FixtureRng};

